title: Muhammad Ahmad Chattha wins PP-36 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Independent Candidate Muhammad Ahmad Chattha has won the election from Punjab Assembly constituency PP-36 Wazirabad-II by securing 87,549 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was PML-N Adnan Afzal Chattha who bagged 49,228 votes.
Votersâ€™ turnout remained 51.25 percent.
